survey_response.review_text: **** ******* * **** **** **** ******* She is very experienced and communicates very clearly and kindly! Dr Sheetal is an excellent dentist! She takes her time with every patient and is highly considerate of your comfort and well-being. No sign of sensitivity or issues after my cavity fillings! Which I usually have problems with. Dentist appointments never ran as smoothly as this!

Dr. Sheetal has an art of making you feel comfortable on the dentists chair. The way she explains the problem with your teeth is worth listening to. She in her own way conveys to you why you need to take care of your teeth regularly and how important it is to have healthy teeth.
My personal experience with cavities is that its really painful when we delay going to a dentist, but the relief you get after going to a dentist is truly great.
When Dr. Sheetal is treating you for your teeth you forget you are sitting on a dentists chair, now that to me is a wonderful experience.

I highly recommend Dr.Sheetal Shetty *** **** ******* * **** **** I have had 3 Root canal's and got partial dentures which are a perfect fit. I keep coming back though I live right on the opposite part of the town ,it is a 45 minutes drive,it is worth the drive. The doctor has this dental vibe you Will not feel the pain at all, she is very ******** *** caring. The clinic is very easy to find and is hi-tech. Now my wife and son also regularly visit the clinic. I love the way the doctor has a discussion with you to explain why and how a procedure is done. I highly recommend you to come to this clinic for your Dental Needs

I would definitely recommend Dr.Sheetal to others. I was suffering from horrible toothache and that's why I visited her. She gave a detailed analysis of the situation and was also very patient throughout the session. She also offered alternatives to decide the course of the treatment. I had a good experience with Dr.Sheetal.

** ******* ****** ** ****** ************* *** ** ******** ** *** *********  She has always explained the root causes, the options of treatment and advises the best for your dental health.  
It helps that she’s a lovely person with a reassuringly perfect smile.  
And most of my dental issues are either handled by her or any of the specialists she calls in.  Highly teccomneded for the central location and ease in getting appointments.

Dr Sheetal was extremely patient and first heard me out completely, then went on to explain the cause and the diagnosis and made sure I understood the process completely which helps a lot. She kept checking throughout if the procedure hurt or if I was uncomfortable so that we can take a break.

I found the location of the clinic very convenient with parking available. The receptionist was friendly and magazines were there to read. Waited only for 5 minutes. Met the doctor, after a thorough examination, explained the procedure, cost involved including follow up visits.
Once the procedure was done , she followed with calls asking about my recovery.
I also found the clinic extremely clean.
Thank you.

Dr Sheetal is extremely patient , ******* *** makes the effort to explain everything in detail. For the first time I left a dental clinic feeling good instead of feeling traumatized. I would recommend Dr Sheetal to everybody who needs any kind of dental care

Dr Sheetal is the most comforting dentist i have ever met. She is very friendly and has pleasant personality. She is a thorough professional and she explains everything very clearly any your problems, suggests the treatements and lets you choose your treatment explaining the pros and cons of each. She is the dentist of choice me, my family and even friends now.

Dr. sheetal is quite awesome. She is a minimalist in the sense that she doesn't recommend unnecessary procedures. Her work is of high quality and follow up reminders are prompt. I have had filling, root canal, and implants done by her, very pleased. Also she keeps meticulous record of all past patient context including history, complications etc. Personalized dentistry at it's best !!

Dr Sheetal Shetty is a competent Dentist.Her diagonis is spot on! She was articulate in her explanation  of the procedure.She was gentle and patient during the treatment.Both my children had their orthodontic treatment at her clinic.We have been visiting her clinic for a number of years.All our family members are her patients due to these factors.

On my several visits for treatment at Dr.  Sheetal's clinic, I was very impressed with the treatment, the communication, the time management and the friendly atmosphere. 
I have found Dr.  Sheetal very gentle, kind & very competent and have recommended her to many of my friends who have been equally
or more satisfied.
